lead_paragraph: A Spanish left-hander moved into the quarter-finals of the French Open on Sunday. No surprise there, although his name was not Rafael Nadal but Albert Ramos-Vinolas.

headline.print_headline: Spanish Left-Hander in French Open Quarters but It Is Not Nadal
